  "section_name": "Investment Recommendation & Outlook",
  "text": "Adobe's core financial metrics support a constructive medium-term outlook. The company maintains exceptional profitability with Q4 2025 gross margins at 88.92% [K003], operating margins at 36.50% [K004], and free cash flow margins reaching 50.47% [K011]. EBITDA generation has remained consistent, with Q4 2025 EBITDA at $2,448 million [C016] compared to $2,462 million in Q3 2025 [C024]. Management's sustained commitment to innovation is evident in R&D spending of $1,098 million in Q4, representing 17.73% of revenue [K007, C018, C012].",
